ar.','http://sourceforge.net/projects/jazzy/',15,1495,1595,'-6.27'),(45545,63,'Programmers Notepad','Programmers Notepad is a powerful text editor featuring syntax highlighting, project management, a great user interface and much more.','http://sourceforge.net/projects/pnotepad/',5,10288,11215,'-8.27'),(79945,63,'Kile KDE LaTeX Editor','Kile is a LaTeX source editor, TeX shell that simplifies the creation of LaTeX documents.','http://sourceforge.net/projects/kile/',2,2413,1858,'29.87'),(85104,63,'PyPE (Python Programmers Editor)','PyPE (Python Programmers Editor) was written in order to offer a lightweight but powerful editor for those of you who think emacs is too much and idle is too little.  Syntax highlighting is included out of the box, as is multiple open documents via tabs.','http://sourceforge.net/projects/pype/',1,659,504,'30.75'),(92412,63,'The LaTeX Beamer Class','The beamer class is a LaTeX class for creating presentations using a video projector. It offers incremental display, prearranged themes, automatic table of contents, navigation bars, bibliographies, and other features. Can be used with pdflatex and LyX.','http://sourceforge.net/projects/latex-beamer/',1,9749,7876,'23.78'),(95078,63,'cssed','cssed is an scriptable and modular GTK2 CSS editor and syntax validator, written for the Linux platform, to help web developers to maintain and create CSS stylesheets for web publishing. There are versions of cssed for MacOsX and Win32, and BSD. ','http://sourceforge.net/projects/cssed/',2,4831,1231,'292.45'),(95717,63,'Notepad++','Notepad++ is a generic source editor (it tries to be anyway) and Notepad replacement written in C++ with the win32 API. The aim of Notepad++ is to offer a slim and efficient binary with a totally customizable GUI.','http://sourceforge.net/projects/notepad-plus/',5,85312,66905,'27.51'),(110857,63,'Smultron','Smultron is a text editor written in Cocoa with many of the features that you might need.','http://sourceforge.net/projects/smultron/',1,8151,3421,'138.26'),(128318,63,'A set of linguistics tools','Linguistico is a linguistics tools project based on Italian language, but can be used also by other languages. Tools are: dictionaries, thesaurus, words definitions, scripts, programs, ... For: OpenOffice.org ThunderBird Mozilla MySpell MyThes Aspell','http://sourceforge.net/projects/linguistico/',2,3397,2545,'33.48'),(148869,63,'WYM editor','Web-based WYSIWYM editor (What You See Is What You Mean), which goal is to produce XHTML-CSS compliant code. WYM editor lets the writer concentrate on the structure and the content of the document, not on the visual layout.','http://sourceforge.net/projects/wym-editor/',2,97,67,'44.78'),(152555,63,'Portable NVU','Portable NVU allows you to carry your a complete web editor with you on a USB thumbdrive, iPod, etc. It\'s based on NVU, so it has all the same great features, but there\'s nothing to install.','http://sourceforge.net/projects/portablenvu/',1,8097,5500,'47.22'),(156910,63,'Steganos LockNote','Store your most valuable notes in a LockNote. Hide your everyday notes in a safe place. Application and document in one: the mechanism to encrypt and decrypt a note is part of it. Secure, simple, independent. No installation required.','http://sourceforge.net/projects/locknote/',1,1279,0,'0.00'),(63,18,'Text Editors',NULL,'http://sourceforge.net/softwaremap/trove_list.php?form_cat=63',0,393768,298566,'31.89'),(18,0,'Topics',NULL,'http://sourceforge.net/softwaremap/trove_list.php?form_cat=18',0,8019277,8037189,'-0.22');
